conquered’ population: in the first century after the Conquest it was the commonest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Brace was born before 1145. He had at least 1 son. He died before 1192, in Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"Bef 1145–Bef 1192":"enne 1145–enne 1192","1170–1250":"1170–1250","1145–1192":"1145–1192","Bef 1145":"enne 1145","1145":"1145","1250":"1250","Bef 1192":"enne 1192","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Bef 1145–Bef 1192":"ennen vuotta 1145–ennen vuotta 1192","1170–1250":"1170–1250","1145–1192":"1145–1192","Bef 1145":"ennen vuotta 1145","1145":"1145","1250":"1250","Bef 1192":"ennen vuotta 1192","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Bef 1145–Bef 1192":"avant 1145–avant 1192","1170–1250":"1170–1250","1145–1192":"1145–1192","Bef 1145":"avant 1145","1145":"1145","1250":"1250","Bef 1192":"avant 1192","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Brace est né avant 1145. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé avant 1192, à Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"Bef 1145–Bef 1192":"vor 1145–vor 1192","1170–1250":"1170–1250","1145–1192":"1145–1192","Bef 1145":"vor 1145","1145":"1145","1250":"1250","Bef 1192":"vor 1192","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"William Brace wurde vor 1145 geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb vor 1192 in Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom."},"ht":{"Bef 1145–Bef 1192":"before 1145–before 1192","1170–1250":"1170–1250","1145–1192":"1145–1192","Bef 1145":"before 1145","1145":"1145","1250":